<p id="notice"><%= notice %></p>

  <div class="row">
       <div class="col s12 m6">
         <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
         <div class="card blue-grey darken-1">
           <div class="card-content white-text">
             <span class="card-title"><%= skill.skill %></span>
             <p><%= skill.description %></p>
           </div>
           <div class="card-action">
             <a href="#">Rating: <%= skill.rating %></a>
             <%= link_to 'Projects', skill %>
           </div>
         </div>
         <% end %>
       </div>
       <div class="col s12 m6">
         <h4>About Kiburei,</h4>
         <p>I am lucky to be fullstack software engineer and bachelors degree holder in Computer Technology. I like to think that computers hold the power to
         make the world a better place. I am actively particapting towards this by putting in work and this is why you are probably here. So we can change things together \o/.
         Do have a look at some of my past, current and ongoing projects. Other than computers I love the outdoors</p>
         <div class="references">
           <h5>References</h5>
           <%= link_to 'Add Reference', new_reference_path, class: 'btn', id: 'new_ref', remote: true  %>
           <div id="user_refs">
             <% if @references.any? %>
              <%= render 'references/reference' %>
             <% else %>
              <p>People dont like you</p>
             <% end %>
           </div>
        </div>
       </div>
    </div>
